                </FooterDetails>
                <Header>Projects</Header>
                <Paragraph>ILAB grants help prevent and stop abusive labor practices like the use of child labor and forced labor and human trafficking. ILAB-funded projects also promote compliance by trade partners' with the labor requirements of U.S. trade agreements and preference programs.</Paragraph>
            </EntitySourceOfInformation>
